Hylian
All of them.
-------------------

The native peoples of Hyrule. Even in the face of adversity, they remain hopeful for the most part... though, they are far from immune to tragedy...


Stats
-------------------
Any Physical, +2.
Any Mental, +2.
Any, -2. Hylians are too varied to have any predictable stats.

